"H-maxima (um)" = "H 极大值 (um)";
"Minimum seed distance (um)" = "最小种子距离 (um)";
"Watershed compactness" = "分水岭紧致度";
"Post-resplit multiplier" = "后重分割倍数";
"Minimum nucleus diameter. Increasing it removes small noise but may drop true small nuclei. Check Fixed in advanced scan to keep this value locked." = "最小细胞核直径。增大该值可去除小噪声，但可能丢失真实的小细胞核。在高级筛选中勾选固定以锁定此值。";
"Maximum nucleus diameter. Lower values reject large objects; higher values allow larger nuclei or clumps. Check Fixed in advanced scan to keep this value locked." = "最大细胞核直径。较低值会排除大对象；较高值允许更大的细胞核或团块。在高级筛选中勾选固定以锁定此值。";
"Background correction radius. Larger values remove slow-varying background more strongly; smaller values preserve raw intensity." = "背景校正半径。较大值会更强地去除缓慢变化的背景；较小值会保留原始强度。";
"Smoothing strength. Larger values reduce noise but blur borders and can merge adjacent nuclei." = "平滑强度。较大值可减少噪声，但会模糊边界并可能合并相邻细胞核。";
"Local background window. Larger values behave more globally; smaller values adapt to local intensity changes." = "局部背景窗口。较大值更接近全局处理；较小值更能适应局部强度变化。";
"Threshold offset. Lower or more negative values usually detect more nuclei; higher values are stricter." = "阈值偏移。较低或更负的值通常会检测更多细胞核；较高值更严格。";
"Peak prominence. Larger values are more conservative; smaller values keep weaker nuclei." = "峰值显著度。较大值更保守；较小值会保留较弱的细胞核。";
"Minimum distance between candidate centers. Larger values reduce over-splitting; smaller values allow dense nuclei." = "候选中心之间的最小距离。较大值可减少过度分割；较小值允许更密集的细胞核。";
"Watershed compactness. Larger values make regions more regular; smaller values follow intensity shape more closely." = "分水岭紧致度。较大值使区域更规则；较小值更贴近强度形状。";
"Post-processing split strength. Larger values split touching objects more aggressively; smaller values are more conservative." = "后处理分割强度。较大值会更积极地分离接触对象；较小值更保守。";

