"Fills small gaps between neighboring same-type cells before ROI detection. Higher values merge nearby islands into broader regions." = "在 ROI 检测前填补相邻同类型细胞之间的小间隙。较高值会将附近岛状区域合并为更宽的区域。";
"Expands the final ROI boundary outward from the selected cell type. Higher values place the contour farther from the cells." = "从所选细胞类型向外扩展最终 ROI 边界。较高值会使轮廓离细胞更远。";
"Drops small ROI fragments after closing. Increase this to remove tiny regions; decrease it to keep smaller structures." = "闭合后移除较小的 ROI 碎片。增大该值可移除微小区域；降低该值可保留较小结构。";
"Keeps only ROI components containing at least this many selected cells. Higher values suppress sparse components." = "仅保留至少包含此数量所选细胞的 ROI 组件。较高值会抑制稀疏组件。";
"Smooths and simplifies contour extraction before drawing. Higher values are faster and lighter, but less detailed." = "绘制前平滑并简化轮廓提取。较高值更快、更轻量，但细节较少。";
"Controls contour thickness in the displayed and exported figures." = "控制显示图和导出图中的轮廓粗细。";
"Controls whether the contour is solid, dashed, dash-dot, or dotted." = "控制轮廓使用实线、虚线、点划线或点线。";
"Use a fixed boundary color, or enable cell-type-specific colors so each ROI contour matches its source cell type." = "使用固定边界颜色，或启用细胞类型专属颜色，使每个 ROI 轮廓与其来源细胞类型一致。";
"Bridges small gaps between the selected cells. Increase this only when one selected cell group should become a smoother continuous ROI." = "连接所选细胞之间的小间隙。仅当一组选定细胞需要形成更平滑的连续 ROI 时增大该值。";
"Expands the adjusted ROI outward after it is rebuilt from selected cells. Keep it low for boundaries that stay close to the selected cells." = "根据所选细胞重建后向外扩展调整后的 ROI。若希望边界贴近所选细胞，请保持较低值。";
"Removes tiny fragments from the adjusted ROI. Set to 0 when drawing small local regions." = "从调整后的 ROI 中移除微小碎片。绘制小型局部区域时请设为 0。";
"Keeps connected adjusted ROI components that contain at least this many selected seed cells." = "保留至少包含此数量所选种子细胞的连通调整后 ROI 组件。";
"Controls boundary simplification for the adjusted preview and export. Lower values preserve more local detail." = "控制调整后预览和导出的边界简化程度。较低值可保留更多局部细节。";

